data.description: Nice corner house with a beautiful tree in Katy Texas. It has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathroom and a spacious living room where you will live memorable events with your family and friends. The primary bedroom has an in-suite bath with separate standing shower and jetted tube with a walking closet.  Its practical kitchen features fornica counter tops, walk in pantry and gas oven will let you cook delicious dinners for all the family. On the backyard you will have plenty of space for some outside furniture and a BBQ grill. The school it's a walking distance from the house. It's convenient location its close from grocery shops and restaurants. Feel free to visit it since it won't last long.
